<HEAD weight="bold"  justified="center" >
WHY HAVE YOU BEEN
</HEAD>


<BLOCK justified=center>

<EMPH weight="bold">
PRESCRIBED CELECTOL?
</EMPH>

</BLOCK>


<BLOCK>
CELECTOL is used to lower your blood pressure.
</BLOCK>


</DIV>
<DIV type=2>

