<EMPH  weight="bold"  uline="plain">
before
</EMPH>
 taking any of the tablets.
</BLOCK>


<LIST type="bulleted">

<ITEM>

<BLOCK>
Are you sensitive or allergic to celiprolol or any other beta-blockers?
